menu "Field Pocket Watch"

    config I2C_MASTER_FREQUENCY
        int "I2C master bus frequency (Hz)"
        default 400000
        help
            Clock speed for the shared I2C peripheral bus (FT3168 touch,
            AXP2101 PMU, and in later steps the QMI8658 IMU and PCF85063 RTC).
            The board support package uses this value for the touch
            controller's I2C speed. 400 kHz (fast mode) is the board default.

endmenu
